>So, all name calling aside, all backpeddling and cowards guised in the form of mockery of TCE in the past, will you flee like a pack of injured pups when we declare war on you?<P>Admittedly, when you war us your entire existance on Sullon will become that war.  We'll hunt you like deer with every last effort, we'll rape you at your spawn point, we'll make it a habit to train you into oblivion.  That is war.  It's not nice, it's war.<P>Tell me you'll accept our challenge, or else you shall remain forever a coward guild.  You will flee us in Shadowbane just as you flee us now, then race to your forums to spout how we aren't worth your time and declare that you seek a better foe.  Truth being, you'll never have a worthwhile foe unless it bears the semblance of a 7 year old child carrying a lolipop that you can gank from behind.<P>War, or STFU.  You have proven nothing to anyone, and you whimper before a threat.  If we are so easily beaten, do so until we retreat.  <P>Let us test the strength of your quest to the top, and see how it compares to some of the PvP and EQ war experienced minds of the empire.<P>  
